Subject: [PATCH v2 1/4] Bluetooth: Remove superfluous call to hci_conn_check_pending()
Date: Mon,  8 Jan 2024 19:39:33 +0100
Message-ID: <20240108183938.468426-2-verdre@v0yd.nl>
